## Pending — full image run not yet started

The script is ready and tested. The full run (~687 fragrances) was not started this session because the user paused to prepare the handover.

**Full run command:**
```bash
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=<service_role_key> \
  npx ts-node --compiler-options '{"module":"CommonJS"}' \
  scripts/fetch-fragrance-images.ts
```

- Chromium window will be visible for the full duration (~2–2.5 hours at ~12 s/fragrance)
- Failures logged to `image-fetch-failures.log`
- Already-processed fragrances (non-null `imageUrl`) are skipped automatically
- Dior Sauvage already has `imageUrl` set — will be skipped on the full run

**Open decision:** the og:image Fragrantica serves is a social card (`en-social-{id}.jpeg`) rather than a clean bottle shot (`fimgs.net/mdimg/perfume/375x500.{id}.jpg`). The user did not confirm which to use before ending the session — confirm at next session start before running.

